3 docker image ls command is used to list all the images in the host 
4 5d118015902f81257aaf639aadc130259632ebe86b1b4dd88f59b4f9a337f872 container id of nginx image
5 docker container run nginx
6 docker comntainer ls command will give you the list of all the containers running
7 docker container ls - a command will give you list of all running and stopped container
8 docker inspect nginx to inspect and get the full container id 5d118015902f81257aaf639aadc130259632ebe86b1b4dd88f59b4f9a337f872
9 docker inspect container_name to inspect the container and find out the image layers used in building the container 3 layers are used in building nginx image
10 docker image pull tomcat:7.0.103
11 docker container run tomcat
