15 docker inspect tomcat will give the info about the container it has the attribute size where we can check the size
16 docker inspect tomcat under env section we will get a list of all the environment variables setup for the image 
17 docker port tomcat to get the list of ports the container is exposed too
18 docker container run -d -p 8080:5001 tomcat
